{
  "stem": "1292.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He gave me the chance-- the stamp, and I took my sister and my mother from the transport.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I brought them home, and I said, please don't go out now because they was short of taking the-- there was a quota.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So many people did have to be in the transport, and they were short of the people to transport.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so I begged them not to come out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They did live with my grandmother together and the Gestapo was running and taking all the old people, you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my mother and my sister did think it would be safe to transport my grandmother to hospital.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they did go out to try to get the what they called a-- oh god, the thing what they would put sick people on.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What do you call that?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Stretcher.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Stretcher.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Stretcher.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sorry.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "See?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mustn't get too excited because then the words are missing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And well they did get the stretcher.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they-- my sister and my mother went to hospital to put my grandmother there and when the hospital was taken all to the transport later, but they did think, being human people, that the sick people would be not taken to the transport.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway it was-- we didn't know what the transport.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They said the transport is to take people to work to a different place, right?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyway-- Did you believe that?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were skeptical, but we didn't have evidence, you see?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were skeptical because how could-- we knew what happened to the German Jews, we knew-- so we knew it's a bad time and bad news for the Jews.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyway, and then my grandmother was taken with the whole hospital to the transport or whatever.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
